<paragraph blockId="21.[160,1155,448,613]" box="[160,409,448,474]" pageId="21" pageNumber="286">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,448,474]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="286">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[160,1155,448,613]" pageId="21" pageNumber="286">Body elongate, narrow, background colour violet or pink. Rhinophores and oral tentacles smooth, white apically with degraded white punctuation. Cerata smooth, long, translucent, with digestive gland visible in orange; white apically, presenting profuse white punctuation.</paragraph>
